reviewText:
Yeah, I obviously made a mistake purchasing this disc, bigtime. This wasn't even worth the $11 or so I paid for it and I used my amazon giftcard, what ?! Please, under no circumstance let the title fool you, it's not erotic and it's not sexy, period. The models, if you wish to call them that are not really hot or attractive, their not even  lukewarm at best. Not only that, the entire time on this disc is less than 20 some minutes, total rip-off ! So, if you're looking for something erotic and sexy, avoid getting this tripe, it's not worth wasting your money on.

There's plenty of other decent dvds of this category to choose from, rhis however is not. Oh before I forget, a second disc came with it, supposedly a comedy of sorts, nothing was funny as I pulled my own hair out.
